==English==
===Noun===
'''[[carbon]] [[dioxide]]'''
{{wikipedia}}
#A [[colourless]], [[odourless]] [[gas]] formed during [[respiration]] and [[combustion]] and [[consumed]] by [[plant]]s during [[photosynthesis]]; used in [[refrigeration]], [[carbonated]] [[beverage]]s, [[fire extinguisher]]s etc
#{{chemistry}} The normal [[oxide]] of [[carbon]], CO<sub>2</sub>; a gas that [[solidifies]] at &minus;78 °C; [[dissolve]]s in [[water]] to form [[carbonic acid]], and [[react]]s with [[base]]s to form [[carbonate]]s

====Related Terms====
*[[carbon monoxide]]
*[[silicon dioxide]]

